    >
    </div>
    <h2
      class="font-mono text-xs/5 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 data-[dark]:text-gray-400"
    >
      Meet the team
    </h2>
    <h3
      class="mt-2 text-pretty text-4xl font-medium tracking-tighter text-gray-950 data-[dark]:text-white sm:text-6xl"
    >
      Leadership Team
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-medium text-gray-500">
      Our leadership team is comprised of experienced aviation professionals who
      are passionate about aviation and committed to providing the highest level
      of training and support to our students.
    </p>
    <ul role="list" class="mx-auto mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <li>
        <ImageComp
          imageAlt="Bill Macon"
          imagePath="/src/assets/images/bill_macon_300.webp"
          styles="w-11/12 max-w-lg h-[30rem] object-cover rounded-xl"
        />
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-main-black font-semibold">
          Bill Macon
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-500 font-semibold">
          Managing Director
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-500">
          Bill comes from a family with a long history of aviation in St. Louis
          Bill began his flight training when he acquired Ideal Aviation in
          2011.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <ImageComp
          imageAlt="Kimberly Nagel"
          imagePath="/src/assets/images/kimberly_300.webp"
          styles="w-11/12 max-w-lg h-[30rem] object-cover rounded-xl"
        />
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-main-black font-semibold">
          Kimberly Nagel
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-500 font-semibold">
          Director of Administration
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-500">
          Kimberly Nagel is a management and accounting professional and joined
          Ideal Aviation in 2012. Kimberly has flown a variety of aircraft.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <ImageComp
          imageAlt="Jim Moseley"
          imagePath="/src/assets/images/jim_300.webp"
          styles="w-11/12 max-w-lg h-[30rem] object-cover rounded-xl"
        />
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-main-black font-semibold">
          Jim Moseley
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-500 font-semibold">
          Chief Flight Instructor / Director of Operations
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 max-w-lg text-sm/6 text-gray-500">
          Jim graduated Magna-Cum-Laude from Saint Louis University with a B.S.
          in Flight Science. He and was awarded the 2018 Flight Instructor of
          the year in the St. Louis area.
        </p>
      </li>
